The paper presents an intelligent user interface model for exploring complex databases using a 3D metaphor. This involves grouping database elements into rooms based on their semantic properties and relationships, and organizing the museum based on user interactions and centers of interest. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Databases (cs.DB), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
